OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1777233953
OL,3,CTeaching assistant shared indecent
OL,4,Cimages of pupils with boyfriend
OL,6,FA teaching assistant who took indecent
OL,7,Fphotographs of pupils and sent them to
OL,8,Fher boyfriend has been jailed.
OL,10,FPamela Martin, 44, was working at a
OL,11,Fschool in South Yorkshire when she
OL,12,Ftook the pictures and shared them with
OL,13,F41-year-old Christopher O'Kane.
OL,15,FThe couple, of Lakeside Drive,
OL,16,FScunthorpe, admit child sex offences
OL,17,Fand have been jailed for seven years.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
