PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1777233953
OL,3,CTeaching assistant shared indecent
OL,4,Cimages of pupils with boyfriend
OL,6,FDet Con Helena Allison, of Humberside
OL,7,FPolice, said: "Martin and O'Kane are
OL,8,Fperverted criminals, and I am
OL,9,Freassured that they are now behind
OL,10,Fbars."
OL,12,FGrimsby Crown Court heard police began
OL,13,Fan investigation after a report O'Kane
OL,14,Fhad sent suggestive messages online
OL,15,Findicating an interest in children.
OL,26,@oD@OOU
