PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1777233953
OL,3,CTeaching assistant shared indecent
OL,4,Cimages of pupils with boyfriend
OL,6,FHe was arrested in December 2025 and
OL,7,Fhad his devices seized by detectives,
OL,8,Fwho found messages between him and
OL,9,FMartin, relating to the sexual abuse
OL,10,Fof children. Martin was arrested the
OL,11,Ffollowing month.
OL,13,FIndecent images were then found on her
OL,14,Fphone, along with sexual messages
OL,15,Fbetween her and O'Kane.
OL,17,FFurther investigation found Martin had
OL,18,Ftaken pictures of students while
OL,19,Fworking as a teaching assistant.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
