PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1777233953
OL,3,CTeaching assistant shared indecent
OL,4,Cimages of pupils with boyfriend
OL,6,FMartin and O'Kane both pleaded guilty
OL,7,Fto three counts of making an indecent
OL,8,Fimage of a child, two counts of
OL,9,Fdistributing an indecent image of a
OL,10,Fchild, possession of an extreme
OL,11,Fpornographic image and publishing an
OL,12,Fobscene article.
OL,14,FAlong with their prison sentences they
OL,15,Fwere given indefinite sexual harm
OL,16,Fprevention orders and will be on the
OL,17,FSex Offenders Register for life.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
