PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1777233953
OL,3,CTeaching assistant shared indecent
OL,4,Cimages of pupils with boyfriend
OL,6,FDet Con Allison added: "I hope the
OL,7,Fsentence given today sends a clear
OL,8,Fmessage that we will not tolerate
OL,9,Fanyone preying on children for their
OL,10,Fown sick sexual gratification.
OL,12,F"If you commit child sex offences, we
OL,13,Fwill do everything in our power to
OL,14,Fbring you to justice for your crimes.
OL,16,F"Martin took advantage of her role in
OL,17,Fa school to create indecent images of
OL,18,Fchildren, at a time when her victims
OL,19,Fand their families trusted her, as a
OL,20,Fprofessional, to look after them.
OL,26,@nD@XOUxD@AOU
